{"title":"Tout Terrain Celebrates 20 Years With Iconic Silk Road Limited Edition","link":"https://theradavist.com/tout-terrain-celebrates-20-years-with-iconic-silk-road-limited-edition/","date":1747911581000,"content":"<p><em>Designed for a life on two wheels and adventures that have no end, the <a href=\"https://tout-terrain.de/en/bikes/expedition/silkroad/anniversary-edition?mc_cid=5610cdad28&amp;mc_eid=170346835a\" target=\"_blank\">Silkroad</a> from <a href=\"https://theradavist.com/search/tout+terrain/\" target=\"_blank\">Tout Terrain</a> has been circumnavigating the globe in one form or another for over two decades. This classic touring all-rounder with integrated, bomb-proof rear rack has proven to be a stalwart design among long-distance touring machines.</em></p>\n<p><span></span></p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/05/2025_Tout_Terrain_20th_Anniversary-4.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/05/2025_Tout_Terrain_20th_Anniversary-4.jpg?w=300&amp;quality=75 800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/05/2025_Tout_Terrain_20th_Anniversary-4.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/05/2025_Tout_Terrain_20th_Anniversary-4.jpg?w=800&amp;quality=75\" /><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/05/2025_Tout_Terrain_20th_Anniversary-2.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/05/2025_Tout_Terrain_20th_Anniversary-2.jpg?w=300&amp;quality=75 800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/05/2025_Tout_Terrain_20th_Anniversary-2.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/05/2025_Tout_Terrain_20th_Anniversary-2.jpg?w=800&amp;quality=75\" /><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/05/2025_Tout_Terrain_20th_Anniversary-3.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/05/2025_Tout_Terrain_20th_Anniversary-3.jpg?w=300&amp;quality=75 800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/05/2025_Tout_Terrain_20th_Anniversary-3.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/05/2025_Tout_Terrain_20th_Anniversary-3.jpg?w=800&amp;quality=75\" /></p>\n<p>To celebrate 20 years in business, Tout Terrain is releasing 100 Silkroad Xplore II numbered editions, featuring 29” wheels and exclusive equipment.</p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/05/2025_Tout_Terrain_20th_Anniversary-5.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/05/2025_Tout_Terrain_20th_Anniversary-5.jpg?w=650&amp;quality=75 640w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/05/2025_Tout_Terrain_20th_Anniversary-5.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75 1800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/05/2025_Tout_Terrain_20th_Anniversary-5.jpg?w=2000&amp;quality=75\" /></p>\n<p>The anniversary edition of the Silkroad Xplore shines in the exclusive British Racing Green Metallic color with bronze-colored anniversary decals that set noble accents and give the bike a timeless elegance. This special paint finish is complemented by honey-colored ergonomic grips while its Brooks B17 gives every bike an unmistakable, stylish character.</p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/05/2025_Tout_Terrain_20th_Anniversary-7.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/05/2025_Tout_Terrain_20th_Anniversary-7.jpg?w=400&amp;quality=75 800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/05/2025_Tout_Terrain_20th_Anniversary-7.jpg?w=1000&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/05/2025_Tout_Terrain_20th_Anniversary-7.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" /><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/05/2025_Tout_Terrain_20th_Anniversary-6.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/05/2025_Tout_Terrain_20th_Anniversary-6.jpg?w=400&amp;quality=75 800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/05/2025_Tout_Terrain_20th_Anniversary-6.jpg?w=1000&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/05/2025_Tout_Terrain_20th_Anniversary-6.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" /></p>\n<p>At its heart is the Pinion P-Line, a high-precision shifting technology modeled on sophisticated automotive transmission technology in an elaborately crafted, aluminum housing with an elegant, black look. The P1.18 transmission is unique; with 18 actual gears, the compact gearbox offers an unsurpassed 636% gear range with a ratio that no other gearbox can achieve.</p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/05/2025_Tout_Terrain_20th_Anniversary-1.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/05/2025_Tout_Terrain_20th_Anniversary-1.jpg?w=650&amp;quality=75 640w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/05/2025_Tout_Terrain_20th_Anniversary-1.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75 1800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/05/2025_Tout_Terrain_20th_Anniversary-1.jpg?w=2000&amp;quality=75\" /></p>\n<p>Finally, each model comes equipped with a set of the versatile new Touring Pedal II pedals from Tout Terrain. The Silkroad Xplore II 29 retails for 7,499.00 € via their <a href=\"https://tout-terrain.de/en/bikes/expedition/silkroad/\" target=\"_blank\">website</a> or through select TT dealers.</p>\n<p>The post <a href=\"https://theradavist.com/tout-terrain-celebrates-20-years-with-iconic-silk-road-limited-edition/\">Tout Terrain Celebrates 20 Years With Iconic Silk Road Limited Edition</a> appeared first on <a href=\"https://theradavist.com\">The Radavist</a>.</p>","author":"spencer harding","siteTitle":"The Radavist","siteHash":"96eb481d8084f04a4602bac57874ba717baf56b758f45547b5caf2312da766ef","entryHash":"d0bd5af3465de3ad3294857cc40efee4d668cebe8d483154d699ed61f07415ba","category":"Cycling"}